{"tid":820522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【校服中學生天台性交】商場平台上演動作片　圍觀者：邊間學校？","createTime":"2018-09-15T13:01:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T14:18:03.000Z","uid":160807,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"328f0d71a9af64c679c48b3232c6969d75813a2b","tid":820522,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180915/photo/bkn-20180915142102520-0915_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180915164555\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180915%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180915142102520-0915_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180915164555&h=a38fd1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男生知道自己被攝入鏡後，向圍觀者揮手打招呼<br />\n<br />\n再有學生疑在公眾地方進行「超友誼」行為。兩名身穿校服的男女學生，在沙田一個商場平台的長櫈上攬作一團，以男前女後姿勢，女方校服裙被拉高，男方則有所動作，全程被人拍攝，期間有旁人議論，「真係好過分喎」、「大庭廣眾」、「邊間學校㗎」，男生其後知道自己被攝入鏡，更向圍觀者揮手打招呼。<br />\n<br />\n東網讀者傳來兩段短片，地點疑為沙田一個商場的平台，首段短片中，男女學生依偎一起，女方校服裙被掀起， 男生身體不斷向前推進，片段傳來一陣笑聲，「哈哈哈，影唔影到呀？真係好過分！」<br />\n<br />\n第二段片，男方已撲在女方身上，不斷向下震動，片段傳來數名男女在議論，「嘩大佬！5分鐘有冇咁犀利呀？搞緊條女？大髀震動緊喎！」亦有人說「唔係呀，真係狼得咁緊要？學生嚟喎，邊間學校呀？等阿姐落去扠𢰸佢！」<br />\n<br />\n之後，男生拿出紙巾抹下身，似穿回長褲，並將手指放在口中，其中一位旁觀女士更稱「(佢哋)星期三都嚟過」，故估計該對男女生以此地作陽台不止一次，另有人稱「佢哋唔知我哋影緊？」男生其後獲知被拍攝，更向觀眾揮手示意，但狀似十分尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n東網正向事發的商場管理處了解。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180915/bkn-20180915142102520-0915_00822_001.html?refer=hn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180915%2Fbkn-20180915142102520-0915_00822_001.html%3Frefer%3Dhn2&d=2rD%2FK2NRUovNF2%2BpW7pkU4zZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=e9da485c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180915/bkn-20180915142102520-0915_00822_001.html?refer=hn2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇無格版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541d9cc13faf79f1c204fc45df471e9958030161","tid":820522,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩 連登狗"},{"pid":"6929f48056bfe9a8c5063482c00613658a4a5397","tid":820522,"uid":196145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:07:03.000Z","msg":"都唔知係啲𡃁妹愈黎愈隨便<br />\n定啲𡃁仔呃蝦條招數愈黎愈高章"},{"pid":"4e85fd04268c843ce58b64471bcdcc87523ccb70","tid":820522,"uid":44163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"每次見到我地香港既年青人連扑野既地方都冇，<br />\n就覺得呢個城市好可悲！"},{"pid":"2273f8c0001b20e291c3b8f8c48172232c0e2fcb","tid":820522,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e85fd04268c843ce58b64471bcdcc87523ccb70","tid":820522,"uid":44163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"每次見到我地香港既年青人連扑野既地方都冇，<br />\n就覺得呢個城市好可悲！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/IpIkVLvMS9M/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FIpIkVLvMS9M%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=29004d77&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f00572001da1eb45385e3d21b50dff37cb600775","tid":820522,"uid":179467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:11:01.000Z","msg":"睇戲嗰d阻人扑嘢燒春袋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aafc5906119ac9aa503bb17b6e4a1cc0bfd390cb","tid":820522,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:41:26.000Z","msg":"成功人士"},{"pid":"c8da5c509f635998262d239a93a0e67f82eaa3c2","tid":820522,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T13:56:25.000Z","msg":"拍到又矇又手震，旁白又係trash talk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e93a613f481d6bd22d1925a192156bc083dc763","tid":820522,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:18:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}